snippet.textDisplay: Last time we went diving/spearfishing with the buddy here in SW Florida (100'deep) we encountered a Tiger shark. It was 12'-15' female( looked to be pregnant..).. started circling us on the way up.. We did have 2 gag groupers and 2 nice snappers on the stringer and a lobster in the bag..  It really started to speed up and circle us closer and closer. finally started to come up from bottom.. We had to get out of the water and drive 1 mile away to do our 3 minute brake..  It was beautiful, but too close to like the situation..  You are looking for them? You are cool and crazy.. Love your videos..  Cheers from Sarasota FL
